data.description: This stunning home, located in Kent’s coveted Creekside community, will amaze you with its brilliantly designed open-concept floorplan. This 4 bed + 2.5 bath, 2102 sqft home, welcomes you with high ceilings, freshly painted interior, refinished flooring, and new carpets as you enter. Highlights include: both formal & casual living areas, new cordless blinds, kitchen w/island, SS appliances, new fridge & microwave, tons of cabinet space, and more! Huge Primary Bed w/5-piece suite & views of the pond. Enjoy the Summer nights from the private backyard overlooking the greenbelt, or get cozy by the gas fireplace on those not-so-summer nights. Ease of access to I-5, Hwy 167, Light-Rail, shopping & more, this is the perfect place to call Home!
